OL,3,CTroubled South East Water names new
OL,4,Cchief executive
OL,6,FTroubled supplier South East Water has
OL,7,Fappointed John Halsall as its incoming
OL,8,Fchief executive after its former boss
OL,9,Fannounced plans to step down in the
OL,10,Fwake of major supply outages in Kent
OL,11,Fand Sussex.
OL,13,FMr Halsall has been hired as chief
OL,14,Fexecutive designate and will take over
OL,15,Ffrom David Hinton after regulatory
OL,16,Fapproval and a handover period.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
