OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782200882
OL,3,CTroubled South East Water names new
OL,4,Cchief executive
OL,6,FThe appointment follows the
OL,7,Fannouncement in May that Mr Hinton
OL,8,Fwould resign, just days after former
OL,9,Fchairman Chris Train also stepped
OL,10,Fdown, following a scathing report into
OL,11,Fa series of outages by MPs, who said
OL,12,Fthey had "no confidence" in the
OL,13,Fcompany's leadership.
OL,15,FThousands of customers were left
OL,16,Funable to access tap water, shower or
OL,17,Fflush their toilets during the outages
OL,18,Fbetween November and January.
OL,26,@tD@JOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
