OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782200882
OL,3,CTroubled South East Water names new
OL,4,Cchief executive
OL,6,FThere have been repeated outages
OL,7,Facross Kent and Sussex since then,
OL,8,Fwith tens of thousands left with water
OL,9,Fsupply issues again in May and June.
OL,11,FMr Halsall said: "My priorities are
OL,12,Fclear: responding to customers'
OL,13,Fimmediate concerns around their water
OL,14,Fservice ` delivering immediately on
OL,15,Fthe short-term improvements we can
OL,16,Fmake both today and over the coming
OL,17,Fweeks and months."
OL,26,@sD@ROUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
