OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782200882
OL,3,CTroubled South East Water names new
OL,4,Cchief executive
OL,6,FHe added: "In the longer term, I am
OL,7,Fexcited by the opportunity to deliver
OL,8,Fthe company's largest-ever investment
OL,9,Fprogramme of #2.1 billion.
OL,11,F"I see this investment as a vital step
OL,12,Fto underpinning the provision of the
OL,13,Fpublic water supply, improving
OL,14,Freliability and resilience in the
OL,15,FSouth East."
OL,17,FDry Wells Action, a consumer action
OL,18,Fgroup based in Tunbridge Wells, said
OL,19,Fit will be pushing for a meeting with
OL,20,Fthe new chief executive.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
