PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782200882
OL,3,CTroubled South East Water names new
OL,4,Cchief executive
OL,6,FJonathan Hawker, the campaign group's
OL,7,Fchairman, said: "We're delighted that
OL,8,Fsomebody would take on this very
OL,9,Fdifficult role leading a company that
OL,10,Fhas lost the trust of many of the
OL,11,Fcommunities that it serves.
OL,13,F"We'll be pressing for an urgent face-
OL,14,Fto-face meeting with this new chief
OL,15,Fexecutive to get assurances that
OL,16,Finfrastructure investment and
OL,17,Fimprovement will happen as a matter of
OL,18,Fgreat urgency."
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
