PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782200882
OL,3,CTroubled South East Water names new
OL,4,Cchief executive
OL,6,FMr Halsall previously served on the
OL,7,Fboard of South West Water, was chief
OL,8,Foperating officer at the supplier's
OL,9,Fowner Pennon Group and was also
OL,10,Fpreviously an executive member of
OL,11,FNetwork Rail, where he ran rail
OL,12,Finfrastructure in the South East.
OL,14,FSouth East Water interim chairwoman
OL,15,FLisa Clement said: "South East Water
OL,16,Ffaces significant challenges and
OL,17,Fcustomers, communities and
OL,18,Fstakeholders rightly expect better.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
