OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782200882
OL,3,CTroubled South East Water names new
OL,4,Cchief executive
OL,6,F"John brings a strong track record of
OL,7,Fdelivering transformation programmes,
OL,8,Foperational leadership and a clear
OL,9,Fcommitment to transparency and
OL,10,Fimprovement across different
OL,11,Findustries."
OL,13,FShe added: "The board is confident
OL,14,FJohn will bring the energy, direction
OL,15,Fand focus needed to accelerate
OL,16,Fprogress and deliver the reliable
OL,17,Fservice our customers deserve."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]uD@LOUyD@_O]
